==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Coalite
<hw>Co"a*lite</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To cause to unite or
coalesce.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Time has by degrees blended . . . and <qex>coalited</qex> the
conquered with the conquerors.</q> <rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coalition</ent>⟦br⟧
